    {
      "name": "The Dead Remember",
      "type": "feature",
      "img": "icons/creatures/magical/spirit-undead-ghost-blue.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>When the Oath-Broken drops to 0 Stamina, it whispers one true thing — a fragment of memory from its former life. This has no mechanical effect but can provide lore clues or emotional weight.</p>",
          "director": "<p>Prepare 2-3 whispered memories beforehand. Examples: 'I swore to hold the gate… I swore…', 'Tell my daughter I didn't run', 'The wolf came through the roots… the wolf…'. These fragments can foreshadow Grafvitnir or humanize the undead — these were people.</p>"
        },
        "source": {
